title: RailWorks 61 US Locos ALL in RWP packages
description:
This is all the US Locomotives on Steam except for 2. There are 61 in this package. Missing are PRR GE-44 and 
UP GE-44. I thought they both were good and I goofed UL the PRR one. These have mostly been tested as working well. About 90% tested. They are all single .rwp files to be installed from the package manager. I have included good quality 1080p pictures for each and each one has all the information in a text file. They are all in seperate folders. Some I have upgraded the pictures in the program as well. They were quite dark. The only one I know has a small glitch is the PRR Baldwin Centipede. For some reason the picture does not show up in Steam 2016. It does work well other than that.


Please UL the two missing Locos if you have them and know that they work well. Also I would really like the Cajon Pass Route if someone could UL that as well.

Enjoy and Happy Holidays!



PS if you like high quality music check my list. Only the highest quality MFSL etc
